C, C++ and Java formatting on Vim

If you like to use "powerful" vim, please try
https://github.com/vim-scripts/c.vim.

Setup

First, you need to install astyle: http://astyle.sf.net.

After installing astyle, make sure you add the bin directory to your PATH. Add
the following line to your .vimrc:

  let $PATH .= ":<path_to_the_bin_directory>"
